sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Inference Gateway<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant Envoy as Envoy Data Plane<br/>ext-proc enabled
    participant EPP as EPP (Endpoint Picker)<br/>9002/TCP gRPC
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant vLLM as vLLM Pod (selected)<br/>8000/TCP HTTP

    Note over Client, vLLM: Flow 1: Standard Inference Request (Single Profile)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTP/80 plaintext
    Gateway->>Envoy: Route to InferencePool
    Envoy->>EPP: ext-proc callback<br/>gRPC/9002 plaintext
    EPP->>K8sAPI: Watch InferencePool, Pods<br/>HTTPS/443 SA token
    K8sAPI-->>EPP: Pod list, EndpointSlices
    Note over EPP: Run filter chain<br/>Run scorer chain<br/>Select best pod
    EPP-->>Envoy: Selected pod endpoint<br/>gRPC/9002
    Envoy->>vLLM: Forward inference request<br/>HTTP/8000 plaintext
    vLLM-->>Envoy: Inference response
    Envoy-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTP Response

    Note over Client, vLLM: Flow 2: Disaggregated Prefill/Decode (P/D) Request

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTP/80 plaintext
    Gateway->>Envoy: Route to InferencePool
    Envoy->>EPP: ext-proc callback<br/>gRPC/9002 plaintext
    Note over EPP: PdProfileHandler selects<br/>prefill + decode profiles
    EPP-->>Envoy: Decode pod + x-prefiller-host-port header<br/>gRPC/9002
    Envoy->>vLLM: Forward to Decode Worker<br/>HTTP/8000 plaintext
    Note over vLLM: Decode sidecar forwards<br/>prefill to prefill worker

    participant PrefillWorker as Prefill Worker<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    vLLM->>PrefillWorker: Prefill request<br/>HTTP/8000 plaintext
    PrefillWorker-->>vLLM: Prefill result
    vLLM-->>Envoy: Final decode response
    Envoy-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTP Response

    Note over Client, vLLM: Flow 3: KV-Cache Event Subscription

    participant vLLMEvents as vLLM Instances<br/>5557/TCP ZMQ
    vLLMEvents->>EPP: KV-cache events<br/>ZMQ SUB/5557 plaintext
    Note over EPP: Update KV-cache indexer<br/>for PrecisePrefixCacheScorer
